title: Did Musician Dr. Creep Predict the COVID Pandemic in a 2013 Song?
subtitle: In his 2013 song “Pandemic,” the rapper did sing about a coronavirus.
author: Nur Ibrahim
vclaim: Dr. Creep, a rapper, predicted the 2020 coronavirus pandemic in his 2013 song “Pandemic,” where he sang: “2020 combined with coronavirus, bodies stacking.”
